               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 3ra-125rb)
 -
                     Discourse of St Athanasius on death (fols. 2ra-8rb)
 - Maṣḥaf za-waḍʾāt
                     ʾǝm-ʾIyarusālem “Book that Came from Jerusalem” (fols. 20ra-22ra)
 - Homily
                     by St Jacob of Serug for the funeral of priests and deacons (fols.
                     55vb-60ra)
 - Homily by archbishop ʾabbā Sawiros (fols. 70va-72vb)
 -
                     Homily by ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols. 81vb-85vb)
 -
                     Antiphons (ʾaryām, mawāśǝʾt and mǝlṭān) (fols. 121ra-125rb)
 
 Additio
                     1.</summary>
