                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#125v">f. 125v</locus>: <desc type="OwnershipNote">Ownership note.<q xml:lang="gez"> ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ግንዘት፡ &lt;...&gt; ወርቀ፡
